[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, you <st data-num=\"0339\" class=\"\">coastlands</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">Pay attention</st>, you <st data-num=\"03816\" class=\"\">people</st> who live <st data-num=\"07350\" class=\"\">far away</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st> me from <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">birth</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">commissioned</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">me</st> when my <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother</st> <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">brought</st> me <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">into the world</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">made</st> my <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st> like a <st data-num=\"02299\" class=\"\">sharp</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"02244\" class=\"\">hid</st> me in the <st data-num=\"06738\" class=\"\">hollow</st> of his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">made</st> me like a <st data-num=\"01305\" class=\"\">sharpened</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02671\" class=\"\">arrow</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">hid</st> me in his <st data-num=\"0827\" class=\"\">quiver</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to me, \u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> are my <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, through <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I will <st data-num=\"06286\" class=\"\">reveal</st> my <st data-num=\"06286\" class=\"\">splendor</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">thought</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cI have <st data-num=\"03021\" class=\"\">worked</st> in <st data-num=\"07385\" class=\"\">vain</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">expended</st> my <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">energy</st> for <st data-num=\"01892\" class=\"\">absolutely</st> <st data-num=\"08414\" class=\"\">nothing</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">But</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"0854 03068\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">vindicate</st> me;<p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"0854 0430\">God</st> will <st data-num=\"06468\" class=\"\">reward</st> me.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the one who <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">formed</st> me from <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">birth</st><n id=\"1\" /> to be his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">he did this<n id=\"2\" /> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">restore</st> <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> himself,<p class=\"poetry\">so that <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> might be <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">gathered</st> to him;<p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"03513\" class=\"\">be honored</st><n id=\"3\" /> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">for my <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">is</st> my <st data-num=\"05797\" class=\"\">source of strength</st><n id=\"4\" />\u2014</p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>, \u201cIs it too <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">insignificant</st> a task for you to <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> my <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">reestablish</st> the <st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribes</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">restore</st> the <st data-num=\"05336\" class=\"\">remnant</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> you a <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">light</st> to the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so you can <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">bring</st><n id=\"4\" /> my <st data-num=\"03444\" class=\"\">deliverance</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"07097\" class=\"\">remote regions</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">Protector</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, their <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st><p class=\"poetry\">to the one who is <st data-num=\"0960 05315\">despised</st><n id=\"3\" /> and <st data-num=\"08581\" class=\"\">rejected</st><n id=\"4\" /> by <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>,<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> of <st data-num=\"04910\" class=\"\">rulers</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">Kings</st> will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> and <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">rise</st> in respect,<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">princes</st> will <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bow down</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">because of</st> the <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">faithful</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> who has <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st> you.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cAt the <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> I decide to show my <st data-num=\"07522\" class=\"\">favor</st>, I will <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">respond</st> to you;<p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of <st data-num=\"03444\" class=\"\">deliverance</st> I will <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">help</st> you;<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05341\" class=\"\">protect</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> you a <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> mediator for <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">rebuild</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and to <st data-num=\"05157\" class=\"\">reassign</st> the <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">desolate</st> <st data-num=\"05159\" class=\"\">property</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <st data-num=\"0631\" class=\"\">prisoners</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Come out</st>,\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">and to those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> are in <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">dark</st> dungeons,<n id=\"2\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">Emerge</st>.\u2019<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">graze</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">beside</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">roads</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">on <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"08205\" class=\"\">slopes</st> they will find <st data-num=\"04830\" class=\"\">pasture</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07456 06770\">be</st> <st data-num=\"07456\" class=\"\">hungry</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"06770\" class=\"\">thirsty</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">sun\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"08273\" class=\"\">oppressive heat</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">beat down on</st> them,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> one who <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">has compassion on</st> them will <st data-num=\"05090\" class=\"\">guide</st> them;<p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"05095\" class=\"\">lead</st> them <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"04002\" class=\"\">springs</st> of <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> my <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> into a <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">road</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">construct</st> my <st data-num=\"04546\" class=\"\">roadways</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> from <st data-num=\"07350\" class=\"\">far away</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">some</st> come from the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st> and <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">west</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">others</st> from the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"05515\" class=\"\">Sinim</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07442\" class=\"\">Shout for joy</st>, O <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01523\" class=\"\">Rejoice</st>, O <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Let the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> <st data-num=\"06476\" class=\"\">give</st> a <st data-num=\"07440\" class=\"\">joyful shout</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">consoles</st> his <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">shows compassion</st> to the<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06041\" class=\"\">oppressed</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u2018The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> me,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"1\" /> has <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forgotten</st> me.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Can a <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st> <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forget</st> her <st data-num=\"05764\" class=\"\">baby who nurses at</st> her <st data-num=\"05764\" class=\"\">breast</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Can she withhold <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">compassion</st> from the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">child</st> she has <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">borne</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Even if</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">mothers</st><n id=\"3\" /> were to <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forget</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> could <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forget</st> you!<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, I have <st data-num=\"02710\" class=\"\">inscribed</st> your name<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> my <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">palms</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">walls</st> are <st data-num=\"08548\" class=\"\">constantly</st> <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> me.</p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st> <st data-num=\"04116\" class=\"\">hurry</st> back,<p class=\"poetry\">while those who <st data-num=\"02040\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> and <st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\">devastated</st> you <st data-num=\"04480 03318\">depart</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05375 05869 07200\">Look</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">all around</st> you!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of them <st data-num=\"06908 0935\">gather</st> to you.<p class=\"poetry\">As surely as <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">live</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cyou will <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"03847\" class=\"\">wear</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them like <st data-num=\"05716\" class=\"\">jewelry</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you will <st data-num=\"07194\" class=\"\">put</st> them <st data-num=\"07194\" class=\"\">on</st> as if you were a <st data-num=\"03618\" class=\"\">bride</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Yes</st>, your <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> lies in <st data-num=\"02723\" class=\"\">ruins</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">it is <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">desolate</st> and <st data-num=\"02035\" class=\"\">devastated</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> you will <st data-num=\"03334\" class=\"\">be</st> too <st data-num=\"03334\" class=\"\">small</st> to hold your <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and those who <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">devoured</st> you will <st data-num=\"07368\" class=\"\">be far away</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">Yet</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st> born during your <st data-num=\"07923\" class=\"\">time of bereavement</st><p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st> within your <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">hearing</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018This <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st> is too <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">cramped</st> for us,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">make room</st> for us so we can <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live here</st>.\u2019<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Then you will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">think</st> to <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">yourself</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">bore</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> children for me?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> was <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">bereaved</st> and <st data-num=\"01565\" class=\"\">barren</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01473\" class=\"\">dismissed</st> and <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">divorced</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">raised</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> children?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> was <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">left</st> <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">all alone</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0375\" class=\"\">where</st> did <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">children</st> <st data-num=\"0375\" class=\"\">come from</st>?\u2019\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st> I will <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">raise</st> my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">raise</st> my <st data-num=\"05251\" class=\"\">signal flag</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">peoples</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> in their <st data-num=\"02684\" class=\"\">arms</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">carry</st> your <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"03802\" class=\"\">shoulders</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">Kings</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> your children\u2019s<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">guardians</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"08282\" class=\"\">princesses</st> will <st data-num=\"03243\" class=\"\">nurse</st> your children.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">With their <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">faces</st> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> they will <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bow down</st> to you,<p class=\"poetry\">and they will <st data-num=\"03897\" class=\"\">lick</st> the <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">dirt</st> on<n id=\"3\" /> your <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">feet</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Then you will <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">recognize</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>;<p class=\"poetry\">those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"06960\" class=\"\">wait patiently</st> for me are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">put to shame</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Can <st data-num=\"04455\" class=\"\">spoils</st> be <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken</st> from a <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">warrior</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">captives</st> be <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">rescued</st> from a <st data-num=\"06184\">conqueror</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"03588 03541 0559\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">captives</st> will be <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken</st> from a <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">warrior</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04455\" class=\"\">spoils</st> will be <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">rescued</st> from a <st data-num=\"06184\" class=\"\">conqueror</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"07378\" class=\"\">oppose</st> your <st data-num=\"03401\" class=\"\">adversary</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">rescue</st> your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will make your <st data-num=\"03238\" class=\"\">oppressors</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> their own <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">flesh</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"07937\" class=\"\">get drunk</st> on their own <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st>, as if it were <st data-num=\"06071\" class=\"\">wine</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">humankind</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">recognize</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, your <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">Deliverer</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">Protector</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"046\">Powerful One</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  }
